  "title": "Baker (Halal Muffins) | Alexandra / Fusionopolis | Up to $3.2K Gross",
  "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Basic $2,300 - $2,700 + OT + Performance Bonus (PB).</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>5-day work week (44 hours per week) with dedicated morning, lunch, and tea breaks.</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>$500 Transport Allowance + $50 Muslim Allowance (for Muslim staff).</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Earn an extra $50 Allowance when working 6 hours or more on a Sunday.</strong></p></li></ul><h3><strong>Job Summary</strong></h3><p>Join a Halal-certified bakery dedicated to using only the best ingredients for our signature muffins, freshly baked every morning. We are looking for a hands-on Baker with at least 1 year of experience to maintain our high standards of quality and assist in creating exciting new flavors.</p><h3><strong>Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Prepare and bake a variety of muffins and baked goods according to house recipes and standards.</p></li><li><p>Ensure consistent quality, presentation, and taste for all products.</p></li><li><p>Maintain a clean, organized, and hygienic kitchen area at all times.</p></li><li><p>Manage stock levels of ingredients and supplies, and collaborate on developing new muffin flavors and products.</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>1 year of hands-on experience</strong> in a bakery environment.</p></li><li><p>Must be able to stand for long hours (no age limit applies).</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Additional Information</strong></h3><ul><li><p><strong>Locations</strong>:</p><ul><li><p>Alexandra</p></li><li><p>Fusionopolis</p></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Shift Details</strong>: 44-hour work week including rest breaks.</p></li></ul>",
